extendAriaLabel(Button, String) - Static method in class org.vaadin.addons.aria_button.AriaButton
Sets aria-label attribute to specified button.

If the label text is visible on screen, authors should use AriaButton.extendAriaLabelledBy(Button, String) to set aria-labelledby atrribute instead.
extendAriaLabelledBy(Button, String) - Static method in class org.vaadin.addons.aria_button.AriaButton
Sets aria-labelledby attribute to specified button.

If the label text is not visible on screen, authors should use AriaButton.extendAriaLabel(Button, String) to set aria-label attribute instead.
